high_descs: Turn around and walk until you're even with the right side of the stove off to your left and then turn to face it and walk to it.
Pick up the tea pot on the bottom right burner.
Take a couple steps to your right to stand in front of the sink.
Clean the tea pot in the sink and pick it back up before turning off the faucet.
Put the tea pot back on the bottom right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight halfway then turning left to go towards the stove.
Go closer to the stove and take the tea kettle.
Turn to the right and make a left at the sink.
Place the tea kettle on the right side of the sink and turn on the water. Turn the water off and take the tea kettle out.
Turn left and then make a right to face the side of the stove.
Place the tea kettle on the burner on the front of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Clean the tea kettle to place it on the burner on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the stove.
Pick the tea pot up from the stove.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink, turn the water on and then off and take the tea pot out of the sink.
Go left and stand in front of the stove.
Put the tea pot on the bottom right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on the stove.
